room_title: Escape room "The Bunker Room" by Escape the cLock in Garden City
room_address: 124 N Main St Garden City, KS 67846
room_description: A tour of a historic WWII bunker goes horribly wrong... Locked in the bunker set for self-destruction, you must solve all the puzzles and find a way to unblock the door before the mechanism kicks in and poisonous gas is released. You must work together to save us all from mass destruction!
